channel.description: I'm using Zenith Scape as my base server: Heres the problem. I have my no-ip duc set up (V2.2.1., seems to work better) and utorrent. My ip in my loader.java is correct. is there something in the server i need to change? If so, please tell me, or teamveiw. Thank you.
